{
  "work_slug": "alices-adventures-in-wonderland-by-lewis-carroll-5",
  "work_title": "Alice's Adventures in Wonderland (version 4)",
  "work_author": "Lewis Carroll",
  "audio_file": "audio-04",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/alices_adventures_1005_librivox/wonderland_04_carroll.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "04 - The Rabbit sends in a Little Bill",
  "reader_name": "Eric Leach",
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.717,
  "page_num": 2,
  "page_total": 4,
  "page_start_sec": 248.7,
  "page_end_sec": 488.97,
  "corrected": "claude",
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 248.7,
      "end": 251.22,
      "text": "I almost wish I hadn't gone down that rabbit-hole."
    },
    {
      "start": 252.0,
      "end": 252.28,
      "text": "And yet,"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.6,
      "end": 254.3,
      "text": "and yet it's rather curious,"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.3,
      "end": 254.8,
      "text": "you know,"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.84,
      "end": 255.52,
      "text": "this sort of life."
    },
    {
      "start": 256.32,
      "end": 258.24,
      "text": "I do wonder what _can_ have happened to me!"
    },
    {
      "start": 258.56,
      "end": 260.32,
      "text": "When I used to read fairy-tales,"
    },
    {
      "start": 260.5,
      "end": 262.46,
      "text": "I fancied that kind of thing never happened,"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.82,
      "end": 264.6,
      "text": "and now here I am in the middle of one."
    },
    {
      "start": 265.14,
      "end": 267.02,
      "text": "There ought to be a book written about me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.04,
      "end": 267.62,
      "text": "that there ought,"
    },
    {
      "start": 268.14,
      "end": 269.58,
      "text": "and when I grow up I'll write one."
    },
    {
      "start": 270.9,
      "end": 271.8,
      "text": "But I'm grown up now,"
    },
    {
      "start": 272.08,
      "end": 273.54,
      "text": "she added in a sorrowful tone."
    },
    {
      "start": 274.3,
      "end": 276.46,
      "text": "At least there's no room to grow up any more _here_."
    },
    {
      "start": 278.72,
      "end": 279.0,
      "text": "But then,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 279.12,
      "end": 279.68,
      "text": "thought Alice,"
    },
    {
      "start": 279.84,
      "end": 281.96,
      "text": "shall I _never_ get any older than I am now?"
    },
    {
      "start": 282.72,
      "end": 283.98,
      "text": "That'll be a comfort one way,"
    },
    {
      "start": 284.06,
      "end": 285.18,
      "text": "never to be an old woman,"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.76,
      "end": 287.7,
      "text": "but then always to have lessons to learn."
    },
    {
      "start": 287.84,
      "end": 288.2,
      "text": "Oh,"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.34,
      "end": 289.34,
      "text": "I shouldn't like _that_!"
    },
    {
      "start": 289.76,
      "end": 289.86,
      "text": "Oh,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 290.94,
      "end": 292.02,
      "text": "you foolish Alice!"
    },
    {
      "start": 292.28,
      "end": 293.04,
      "text": "she answered herself."
    },
    {
      "start": 293.88,
      "end": 294.88,
      "text": "How can you learn lessons"
    },
    {
      "start": 294.94,
      "end": 295.38,
      "text": "in here?"
    },
    {
      "start": 295.56,
      "end": 295.84,
      "text": "Why,"
    },
    {
      "start": 295.88,
      "end": 296.98,
      "text": "there's hardly room for _you_,"
    },
    {
      "start": 297.16,
      "end": 299.32,
      "text": "and no room at all for any lesson-books!"
    },
    {
      "start": 300.54,
      "end": 301.54,
      "text": "And so she went on,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 301.56,
      "end": 303.72,
      "text": "taking first one side and then the other,"
    },
    {
      "start": 304.18,
      "end": 305.38,
      "text": "and making quite a conversation"
    },
    {
      "start": 305.38,
      "end": 306.34,
      "text": "of it altogether."
    },
    {
      "start": 306.98,
      "end": 308.72,
      "text": "But after a few minutes she heard a"
    },
    {
      "start": 308.72,
      "end": 310.48,
      "text": "voice outside and stopped to listen."
    },
    {
      "start": 313.18,
      "end": 313.54,
      "text": "Mary Ann!",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 313.64,
      "end": 314.5,
      "text": "Mary Ann!"
    },
    {
      "start": 314.72,
      "end": 315.3,
      "text": "said the voice."
    },
    {
      "start": 315.54,
      "end": 317.6,
      "text": "Fetch me my gloves this moment!"
    },
    {
      "start": 318.72,
      "end": 321.0,
      "text": "Then came a little pattering of feet on the stairs.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 321.51,
      "end": 323.94,
      "text": "Alice knew it was the Rabbit coming to look for"
    },
    {
      "start": 323.94,
      "end": 324.06,
      "text": "her,"
    },
    {
      "start": 324.18,
      "end": 326.08,
      "text": "and she trembled till she shook the house,"
    },
    {
      "start": 326.24,
      "end": 328.56,
      "text": "quite forgetting that she was now about a thousand"
    },
    {
      "start": 328.64,
      "end": 330.0,
      "text": "times as large as the Rabbit,"
    },
    {
      "start": 330.12,
      "end": 332.48,
      "text": "and had no reason to be afraid of it."
    },
    {
      "start": 334.624,
      "end": 335.84,
      "text": "Presently the Rabbit came up",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 336.0,
      "end": 337.6,
      "text": "to the door and tried to open it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 338.0,
      "end": 341.22,
      "text": "but as the door opened inwards and Alice's elbow was pressed hard"
    },
    {
      "start": 341.38,
      "end": 341.84,
      "text": "against it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 341.9,
      "end": 343.56,
      "text": "that attempt proved a failure."
    },
    {
      "start": 344.416,
      "end": 345.7,
      "text": "Alice heard it say to itself,"
    },
    {
      "start": 346.34,
      "end": 347.2,
      "text": "Then I'll go round and"
    },
    {
      "start": 347.2,
      "end": 348.12,
      "text": "get in at the window."
    },
    {
      "start": 349.088,
      "end": 349.76,
      "text": "_That_ you won't,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 349.78,
      "end": 350.24,
      "text": "thought Alice,"
    },
    {
      "start": 350.4,
      "end": 352.54,
      "text": "and after waiting till she fancied she"
    },
    {
      "start": 352.54,
      "end": 354.14,
      "text": "heard the Rabbit just under the window,"
    },
    {
      "start": 354.32,
      "end": 357.04,
      "text": "she suddenly spread out her hand and made a snatch"
    },
    {
      "start": 357.04,
      "end": 357.6,
      "text": "in the air."
    },
    {
      "start": 358.46,
      "end": 359.76,
      "text": "She did not get hold of anything,"
    },
    {
      "start": 360.02,
      "end": 362.12,
      "text": "but she heard a little shriek and a fall,"
    },
    {
      "start": 362.38,
      "end": 363.02,
      "text": "and a crash"
    },
    {
      "start": 363.22,
      "end": 363.81,
      "text": "of broken glass,"
    },
    {
      "start": 364.08,
      "end": 365.86,
      "text": "from which she concluded that it was"
    },
    {
      "start": 365.86,
      "end": 368.14,
      "text": "just possible that it had fallen into a"
    },
    {
      "start": 368.26,
      "end": 368.78,
      "text": "cucumber-frame,"
    },
    {
      "start": 368.92,
      "end": 369.94,
      "text": "or something of the sort."
    },
    {
      "start": 372.3,
      "end": 373.52,
      "text": "Next came an angry voice,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 373.72,
      "end": 374.46,
      "text": "the Rabbit's."
    },
    {
      "start": 374.96,
      "end": 375.16,
      "text": "Pat!"
    },
    {
      "start": 375.42,
      "end": 375.7,
      "text": "Pat!"
    },
    {
      "start": 375.88,
      "end": 376.7,
      "text": "Where are you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 377.64,
      "end": 379.42,
      "text": "And then a voice she had never heard before."
    },
    {
      "start": 380.36,
      "end": 380.96,
      "text": "Sure,"
    },
    {
      "start": 381.1,
      "end": 382.98,
      "text": "I'm here digging for apples,"
    },
    {
      "start": 383.1,
      "end": 383.42,
      "text": "yer honour."
    },
    {
      "start": 384.352,
      "end": 384.96,
      "text": "Digging for apples,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 385.08,
      "end": 385.34,
      "text": "indeed!"
    },
    {
      "start": 385.66,
      "end": 387.14,
      "text": "said the Rabbit angrily."
    },
    {
      "start": 387.72,
      "end": 388.22,
      "text": "Here!"
    },
    {
      "start": 388.4,
      "end": 389.84,
      "text": "Come and help me out of _this_!"
    },
    {
      "start": 390.36,
      "end": 392.08,
      "text": "(Sounds of more broken glass.)"
    },
    {
      "start": 393.42,
      "end": 393.94,
      "text": "Now tell me,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 393.96,
      "end": 394.1,
      "text": "Pat,"
    },
    {
      "start": 394.28,
      "end": 395.3,
      "text": "what's that in the window?"
    },
    {
      "start": 396.14,
      "end": 396.68,
      "text": "Sure,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 396.82,
      "end": 397.68,
      "text": "it's an arm,"
    },
    {
      "start": 397.8,
      "end": 398.16,
      "text": "yer honour."
    },
    {
      "start": 398.58,
      "end": 399.8,
      "text": "(He pronounced it \"arrum.\")"
    },
    {
      "start": 401.408,
      "end": 401.96,
      "text": "An arm,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 401.98,
      "end": 402.58,
      "text": "you goose!"
    },
    {
      "start": 402.76,
      "end": 404.24,
      "text": "Who ever saw one that size?"
    },
    {
      "start": 404.7,
      "end": 404.96,
      "text": "Why,"
    },
    {
      "start": 405.06,
      "end": 406.14,
      "text": "it fills the whole window!"
    },
    {
      "start": 407.488,
      "end": 408.18,
      "text": "Sure, it does,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 408.2,
      "end": 408.58,
      "text": "yer honour,"
    },
    {
      "start": 409.34,
      "end": 410.8,
      "text": "but it's an arm for all that."
    },
    {
      "start": 411.74,
      "end": 412.34,
      "text": "Well,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 412.38,
      "end": 414.24,
      "text": "it's got no business there, at any rate:"
    },
    {
      "start": 414.52,
      "end": 415.42,
      "text": "go and take it away!"
    },
    {
      "start": 416.01,
      "end": 418.18,
      "text": "There was a long silence after this,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 418.28,
      "end": 420.5,
      "text": "and Alice could only hear whispers now and then,"
    },
    {
      "start": 420.62,
      "end": 421.2,
      "text": "such as,"
    },
    {
      "start": 421.41,
      "end": 421.96,
      "text": "Sure,"
    },
    {
      "start": 422.16,
      "end": 422.9,
      "text": "I don't like it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 422.92,
      "end": 423.24,
      "text": "yer honour,"
    },
    {
      "start": 423.32,
      "end": 423.76,
      "text": "at all,"
    },
    {
      "start": 423.84,
      "end": 424.46,
      "text": "at all!"
    },
    {
      "start": 425.03,
      "end": 426.38,
      "text": "Do as I tell you,"
    },
    {
      "start": 426.42,
      "end": 427.13,
      "text": "you coward!"
    },
    {
      "start": 427.63,
      "end": 429.6,
      "text": "and at last she spread out her hand"
    },
    {
      "start": 429.6,
      "end": 431.54,
      "text": "again and made another snatch in the air."
    },
    {
      "start": 432.0,
      "end": 433.94,
      "text": "This time there were _two_ little shrieks,"
    },
    {
      "start": 433.98,
      "end": 435.58,
      "text": "and more sounds of broken glass."
    },
    {
      "start": 436.88,
      "end": 439.42,
      "text": "What a number of cucumber-frames there must be! thought Alice."
    },
    {
      "start": 440.22,
      "end": 441.38,
      "text": "I wonder what they'll do next!"
    },
    {
      "start": 441.8,
      "end": 443.42,
      "text": "As for pulling me out of the window,"
    },
    {
      "start": 443.6,
      "end": 444.58,
      "text": "I only wish they _could_!"
    },
    {
      "start": 445.04,
      "end": 447.1,
      "text": "I'm sure _I_ don't want to stay in here any longer!"
    },
    {
      "start": 448.1,
      "end": 450.52,
      "text": "She waited for some time without hearing anything more.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 451.04,
      "end": 453.18,
      "text": "At last came a rumbling of little cart-wheels,"
    },
    {
      "start": 453.46,
      "end": 456.04,
      "text": "and the sound of a good many voices all talking together."
    },
    {
      "start": 456.47,
      "end": 457.8,
      "text": "She made out the words:"
    },
    {
      "start": 458.88,
      "end": 459.68,
      "text": "Where's the other ladder?"
    },
    {
      "start": 460.18,
      "end": 460.68,
      "text": "Why,"
    },
    {
      "start": 460.74,
      "end": 461.9,
      "text": "I hadn't to bring but one."
    },
    {
      "start": 461.96,
      "end": 462.88,
      "text": "Bill's got the other."
    },
    {
      "start": 463.52,
      "end": 463.72,
      "text": "Bill!"
    },
    {
      "start": 463.88,
      "end": 464.36,
      "text": "fetch it here,"
    },
    {
      "start": 464.48,
      "end": 464.64,
      "text": "lad."
    },
    {
      "start": 464.88,
      "end": 464.98,
      "text": "Here,"
    },
    {
      "start": 466.18,
      "end": 467.18,
      "text": "put 'em up at this corner."
    },
    {
      "start": 468.08,
      "end": 468.28,
      "text": "No,"
    },
    {
      "start": 468.36,
      "end": 469.2,
      "text": "tie 'em together first."
    },
    {
      "start": 469.88,
      "end": 471.32,
      "text": "They don't reach half high enough yet."
    },
    {
      "start": 472.12,
      "end": 472.22,
      "text": "Oh!"
    },
    {
      "start": 472.36,
      "end": 473.26,
      "text": "they'll do well enough."
    },
    {
      "start": 473.32,
      "end": 474.04,
      "text": "Don't be particular."
    },
    {
      "start": 474.38,
      "end": 474.48,
      "text": "Here,"
    },
    {
      "start": 475.32,
      "end": 475.54,
      "text": "Bill!"
    },
    {
      "start": 475.66,
      "end": 476.56,
      "text": "catch hold of this rope."
    },
    {
      "start": 477.42,
      "end": 478.1,
      "text": "Will the roof bear?"
    },
    {
      "start": 478.46,
      "end": 479.82,
      "text": "Mind that loose slate."
    },
    {
      "start": 480.42,
      "end": 480.92,
      "text": "Oh!"
    },
    {
      "start": 481.0,
      "end": 481.52,
      "text": "it's coming down!"
    },
    {
      "start": 481.66,
      "end": 483.44,
      "text": "Heads below! (a loud crash.)"
    },
    {
      "start": 484.34,
      "end": 485.24,
      "text": "Now, who did that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 486.0,
      "end": 486.6,
      "text": "It was Bill,"
    },
    {
      "start": 486.62,
      "end": 487.08,
      "text": "I fancy."
    },
    {
      "start": 487.67,
      "end": 488.97,
      "text": "Who's to go down the chimney?"
    }
  ]
}